DOC.brief_summary: To demonstrate the relative bioequivalence of Cefdinir and Omnicel 250 mg/5 ml fed conditions.
DOC.brief_title: To Demonstrate the Relative Bioequivalence of Cefdinir and Omnicel 250 mg/5 ml Oral Suspension Fed Conditions
DOC.criteria: No clinically significant abnormal finding on physical exam, medical history, or clinical laboratory results on screening. Positive test results for HIV or hepatitis B or C. Treatment for drug or alcohol dependence.
